    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-string S54 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox for maximum driver engagement, transferring power through a variable M-differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term internal health. The chassis has been inspected and reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the powertrain and drivetrain are in peak operating condition, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
