      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it is looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me\u2014super reliable, drives smoothly, and is in really solid shape overall. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so it\u2019s ready for you to hit the road the moment you get the keys. It\u2019s perfect if you want something dependable that still looks great in the driveway. Drop me a message if you have any questions or want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
